org.webcurator.domain.model.auth
Class RolePrivilege

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.auth.RolePrivilege
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class RolePrivilege
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The RolePrivilege class holds all the system privileges that allow access to WCT functions. Privileges are assigned to users via the users role. A RolePrivilege is a mapping from Role to Privilege with an attached scope that defines how widely the privilege can be used. All privilege strings are defined in the Privilege class.
